I.header: Construction work: Genève - La Plaine (SBB CFF FFS)
I.lead: Between Genève and La Plaine on the Genève - Bellegarde (Ain) line, no train services are operating.
I.text:
Construction work: Between Genève and La Plaine on the Genève - Bellegarde (Ain) line, no train services are operating.
Trains are cancelled between Genève and La Plaine / Bellegarde (Ain).
Replacement bus services are operating Genève - La Plaine.
Replacement bus services are operating Genève - Bellegarde (Ain).
Replacement bus services are operating Genève - St-Julien en Genevois.
Passengers travelling from Genève
- to Bellegarde (Ain) / Grenoble / Nice-Ville / Montpellier St-Roch or vice versa travel via Bus - Genève - Bellegarde (Ain).
- to Lyon-Part-Dieu or vice versa travel via Bus Genève - St-Julien en Genevois.
The bus/train connections are guaranteed in Bellegarde (Ain) + St-Julien en Genevois.
Please allow for a longer travelling time.
Duration of construction work from 15.07.2014 02:00 until 24.08.2014 close of services.
Please listen to the loudspeaker announcements in the train.
Please note the information at the station.
The online timetable at www.sbb.ch has been changed.
